<item>
            <title>[LU-16172] o2iblnd: trace every rx/tx message and other debug tweaks</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16172</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Enable tracing of every outgoing rx and incoming tx message when net debug level is set. Add printing of IB connection&apos;s &quot;CM id&quot; and &quot;QP num&quot; to debug messages for easier matching to mlnx driver. Make printing of debug message on o2iblnd connection refcount increment/decrement events compile-time optional. Add compile-time option for dumping detailed connection state info to net debug log.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
